<Data CreatedBy="admin" CreatedOn="634158367083128556" UpdatedBy="admin" UpdatedOn="634274986147549517">
  <Properties />
  <Nodes>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="1"><![CDATA[The example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>The example contains <em>TabControl </em>with displayed tabs in one row.</p><p>Check the 'Multiline' checkbox to see how the TabControl orders the tabs in one and multiples rows.<br /><br />Click on <img height="16" width="16" align="top" alt="Back scroll button" src="/KB/Articles/scrollingpage_kb001/back.png" /> and <img height="16" width="16" align="top" alt="Forward scroll button" src="/KB/Articles/scrollingpage_kb001/forward.png" /> buttons to scroll tab pages.</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="1"><![CDATA[General Info]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2"><![CDATA[<p>The Visual WebGui <em>TabControl </em>contains the <em>Multiline </em>property that indicates how to order tabs - in multiple or single row.</p>]]></Paragraph>
  </Nodes>
</Data>